  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779700/extras/28b7084b814fd06d5cbf29c2d790d23c.poster.avif?t=1746349441\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779700/extras/28b7084b814fd06d5cbf29c2d790d23c.webm?t=1746349441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779700/extras/28b7084b814fd06d5cbf29c2d790d23c.mp4?t=1746349441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Alex is a fan of video-games since he is 7. One night, while he was playing as the storm rages outside, he got his mind and body transferred into his console and TV ! To get out he has to take the place of his beloved heroes : Nario, Pegaman and Lonic and beat the levels !<br><br><strong>Features :</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three different universes with three different gameplays !</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A simple story, but yet animated !</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A game suitable for everyone.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Controller support.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chiptunes music to make you feel nostalgic.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779700/extras/28b7084b814fd06d5cbf29c2d790d23c.poster.avif?t=1746349441\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779700/extras/28b7084b814fd06d5cbf29c2d790d23c.webm?t=1746349441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/779700/extras/28b7084b814fd06d5cbf29c2d790d23c.mp4?t=1746349441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Alex is a fan of video-games since he is 7. One night, while he was playing as the storm rages outside, he got his mind and body transferred into his console and TV ! To get out he has to take the place of his beloved heroes : Nario, Pegaman and Lonic and beat the levels !<br><br><strong>Features :</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Three different universes with three different gameplays !</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A simple story, but yet animated !</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A game suitable for everyone.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Controller support.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chiptunes music to make you feel nostalgic.</li></ul>",
